title: Test
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of students in thousands, with a total of 19 data points.
Overall Number of students in thousands has increased over the Year.

Number of students in thousands is roughly constant from 2000 to 2001, gradually increasing from 2001 to 2005, roughly constant from 2005 to 2008, gradually increasing from 2008 to 2012, roughly constant from 2012 to 2017, and lastly roughly increasing from 2017 to 2018.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2009 and 2010.
Max Number of students in thousands about 1341.35 was recorded at Year 2018
Min Number of students in thousands about 846.6 was recorded at Year 2000
